Dialogue: 0,0:00:-01.00,0:00:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inherited will...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.64,0:00:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The tide of the times...\NPeople's dreams...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.54,0:00:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These things cannot be stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.38,0:00:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as people\Nseek the answer of freedom,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.48,0:00:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,these things will never cease to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.03,0:00:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only believe in the future --\NI don't care if anyone laughs
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.20,0:00:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That racing passion makes you shine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.54,0:00:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too bright,\Nbut I want to gaze at it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.54,0:00:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sense "aesthetics" somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.15,0:00:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really really stuck on you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.55,0:00:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I follow, follow in the footsteps\Nof a dream that resembles no one
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.99,0:00:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until I dramatically get it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.33,0:01:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe In Wonderland!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.14,0:01:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to catch, catch the shape\Nof a dream no one can see
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.44,0:01:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go with you,\Nso passionate feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.58,0:01:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really\Nneed everything to add up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.59,0:01:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than run-of-the-mill daily life,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.76,0:01:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,run for paradise instead
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.36,0:01:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe In Wonderland!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.04,0:01:38.12,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Yuba" "Erumalu" "Nanohana" "Katorea"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.14,0:01:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three years have passed\Nsince a single drop of rain fell
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.14,0:01:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in the kingdom of oases.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.68,0:01:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing hope beyond turmoil,\Nthe people took up weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.88,0:01:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The burning land is now\Nenveloped by a sad bellowing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.88,0:01:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and a mighty swell.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.82,0:01:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vivi tells that Koza, the\Nleader of the rebel army,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.96,0:02:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,possesses a passionate heart and will\Nfight to the death for his friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.69,0:02:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy's party continues its trek\Nthrough the desert toward Yuba,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.70,0:02:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,where the rebel army is gathering.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.44,0:02:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Showdown in a Heat Haze!\NAce vs. the Gallant Scorpion"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.07,0:02:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Popo?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.88,0:02:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.48,0:02:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.42,0:03:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The tattoo on his back...\NNo question about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.16,0:03:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire Fist Ace! He finally showed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.99,0:03:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Portgas D. Ace! How I've\Nbeen longing for this day!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.00,0:03:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--This is all the breakfast we get?!\N--Seconds! Seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.64,0:03:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't act wasteful!\NYou've had enough calories!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.71,0:03:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Luffy! Why, you--!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.51,0:03:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Keep your hands off others' food!\N--C'mon! Gimme food!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.12,0:03:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Don't sweat it!\N--There isn't any more!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.52,0:03:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does this happen at every meal?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.35,0:03:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make eye contact.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.72,0:03:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! Ace-san is cleaning his\Nfork and plate after his meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.93,0:03:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! He's completely different...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.76,0:03:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Damn you! Give it back!\N--No!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.00,0:03:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...from his incompetent little brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.70,0:03:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you'd never guess from\NAce's well-mannered personality
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.87,0:03:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that he has an immense\Nbounty on his head.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.98,0:03:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace-san has a bounty?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.48,0:04:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear it's such a large amount\Nthat bounty hunters around the world
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.88,0:04:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drool at the thought of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.82,0:04:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire Fist Ace of the\NWhitebeard Pirates...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.79,0:04:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirates the world over fear\Nthe mere mention of that name.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.96,0:04:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means this Blackbeard pirate\NAce-san is seriously chasing
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.86,0:04:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,must really be something, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.10,0:04:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blackbeard... The traitor who\Nkilled his own crewmate...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.20,0:04:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like Ace is going to keep\Nchasing him as long as it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.71,0:04:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire Fist Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.35,0:04:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll start off with a little gift from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.55,0:04:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I ain't gonna kill ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.52,0:04:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just gonna blow up that\Nrock you're sitting on first!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.00,0:05:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have my pride! So my aim\Nis to capture you alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.08,0:05:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Let's get going! Today--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.11,0:05:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Dammit! Give it back!\N--What's the big deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.55,0:05:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Knock it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.62,0:05:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...off!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.82,0:05:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Here we go!\N--Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.56,0:05:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now hurry and clean up!\NWe're leaving for Yuba!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.83,0:05:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wow! Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.00,0:05:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Oh no! They saw us!\N--Hurry, big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.74,0:05:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This meat can talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.31,0:05:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What're you talking about, Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.27,0:05:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! The meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.84,0:05:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The meat's running away!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.01,0:05:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Wait, meat!\N--Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.72,0:05:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get back here, meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.96,0:05:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which way?! This way?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.06,0:05:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it, big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.06,0:06:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it good, Chip? It's our first\Nfood in 10 days! Eat it slowly!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.63,0:06:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe we got meat!\NHere, big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.07,0:06:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we never even had\Nany in the Badlands!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.01,0:06:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? You're from the Badlands?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.88,0:06:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From that rustic nowheresville?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.01,0:06:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Who're you?!\N--You can't have the food back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.99,0:06:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Move and you're dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.56,0:06:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm generally not fond\Nof dangerous things, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.36,0:06:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-Big brother!\NHave you shot for reals before?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.33,0:06:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will it really shoot bullets?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.70,0:06:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hell if I know!\NH-Hold on! I'm gonna--!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.67,0:06:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.34,0:06:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.11,0:06:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Play your dangerous games in moderation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.68,0:06:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good little boys should brush\Ntheir teeth before sleepy-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.32,0:06:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-He bounced it back with a rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.79,0:06:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I've never seen\Nanyone so strong before!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.66,0:07:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who're they?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.10,0:07:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a favor to ask!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.06,0:07:10.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's someone I want\Nyou to find and catch!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.94,0:07:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you catch him,\NI'll pay you a million Berries!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.64,0:07:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A million Berries?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.21,0:07:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't pay right away,\Nbut I will pay it when I grow up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.08,0:07:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Find this man!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.22,0:07:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scorpion-sama's ultimate weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.62,0:07:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One hit from this will\Ndemolish that entire rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.06,0:07:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, while Ace is buried under\Nthe rubble, I'll capture him alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.17,0:07:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Light 'er up, Popo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.41,0:07:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn it! It's meat, but it\Nran away! I'll make it pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.78,0:07:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.85,0:07:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you! Why did you do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.35,0:08:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll strangle ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.79,0:08:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.13,0:08:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Hey, boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.80,0:08:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.57,0:08:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that blows up, it'll take\Nhalf of Alabasta with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.47,0:08:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.24,0:08:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! It'll blow the\NGrand Line to the moon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.15,0:08:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Boy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.69,0:08:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.49,0:08:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What happened to the bomb?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.33,0:08:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.40,0:08:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.90,0:08:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're funny, old guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.64,0:08:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, boy! Quit laughing and help me up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.81,0:09:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Upsy-daisy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.45,0:09:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where?! Where is he?! Where'd he go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.32,0:09:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't afford to be playing\Naround at a time like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.86,0:09:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Popo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.06,0:09:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're heading out to where he was!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.96,0:09:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My brother and I've followed\Nhim out here from the Badlands.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.47,0:09:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.47,0:09:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scorpion. A bounty hunter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.47,0:09:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bounty hunter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.94,0:09:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you guys\Nchasing a bounty hunter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.01,0:09:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Well...\N--I have business with him, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.02,0:09:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A man in Yuba defeated Blackbeard.\NHis name was Scorpion.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.49,0:09:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My reason for going\Nto Yuba is to meet him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.62,0:09:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! He defeated Blackbeard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.63,0:09:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy did?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.80,0:10:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, where are we going, old guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.11,0:10:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a very lucky boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.01,0:10:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You get to witness me, the world's\Ngreatest upcoming bounty hunter,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.08,0:10:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,locked in battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.32,0:10:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a bounty hunter, old guy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.19,0:10:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be scared when I say
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.86,0:10:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that I've been on many\Na heart-pounding adventure!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.36,0:10:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've fought epic battles with\Neveryone from Double Barrel Danny
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.36,0:10:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to Hellbattler Luther and they\Nalways begged me for their lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.53,0:10:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! For reals?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.07,0:10:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, but someday it will be!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.27,0:10:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, someday, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.04,0:10:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case,\NI'm gonna beat Fire Fist Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.61,0:10:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone else but him would be a cinch!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.68,0:10:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna beat Ace up,\Nold guy?! That's funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.12,0:10:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now! Don't mock me, boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.56,0:10:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I do something, I don't kid around!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.63,0:11:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Men live for big ambitions!\NI have to show 'em that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.77,0:11:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Show who?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.84,0:11:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here comes Scorpion, the gallant man!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.03,0:11:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I dunno, Ace. Did this Scorpion\Nguy really beat Blackbeard?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.53,0:11:39.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure. The only way\Nto find out is to meet him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.40,0:11:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Ace? You don't mean the real...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.41,0:11:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Fire Fist Ace?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.98,0:11:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Ace?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.35,0:11:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two people. And a bird?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.32,0:11:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.32,0:12:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--They're coming!\N--Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.00,0:12:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There you are, Fire Fist Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.17,0:12:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Scorpion! The indomitable hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.14,0:12:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've come from afar to challenge you!\NLet's fight, fair and square!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.98,0:12:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Scorpion?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.22,0:12:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heya! Are you all here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.18,0:12:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.85,0:12:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you doing there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.03,0:12:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's really him...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.26,0:12:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Fire Fist Ace?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.93,0:12:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, old guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.93,0:12:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! N-No, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.37,0:12:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So sorry! Your luck's run out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.51,0:12:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your heroic saga that's\Ntold on the sea ends today!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.88,0:12:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid! He's the real one!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.81,0:12:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.15,0:12:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is so exciting!\NAce! It's a serious fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.89,0:13:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't pull any punches!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.92,0:13:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't planning to!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.22,0:13:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's something\NI wanna ask him, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.89,0:13:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move aside, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.26,0:13:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with me?!\NDon't wimp out now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.13,0:13:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is nothing!\NI'm invulnerable! I won't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.00,0:13:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not as long as they're waiting for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.57,0:13:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come, Fire Fist Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.04,0:13:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.15,0:13:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-W-W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.93,0:13:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oww! Hot! Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.26,0:13:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-He sent that metal net flying back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.11,0:13:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wouldn't be any fun if it were\Nthat easy to stop Fire Fist Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.74,0:14:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? You seem to have some skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.68,0:14:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our hellish battle is just getting started!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.62,0:14:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Popo! Compressed Extinguisher Gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.09,0:14:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A compressed air gun filled\Nwith extinguisher foam!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.46,0:14:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Wh-What?!\N--Extinguisher?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.10,0:14:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna use this to fill you full\Nof compressed extinguisher foam!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.45,0:14:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but you never had a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.36,0:14:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I expected as much. You lied about\Nbeating Blackbeard, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.66,0:14:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You figured using his name would\Nget me to show up. Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.13,0:15:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Not too\Nshabby of a plan, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.21,0:15:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've fought on even terms this far.\NNow I'm gonna get serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.41,0:15:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No more!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.81,0:15:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.31,0:15:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Eh?!\N--Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.65,0:15:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"D-Dad"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.82,0:15:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.96,0:15:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Dip! Chip!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.23,0:15:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.53,0:15:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! You don't stand a\Nchance against Fire Fist Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.57,0:15:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you two doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.24,0:15:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When did you leave the Badlands?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.78,0:15:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad! Look! Look how big this potato is!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.55,0:15:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! That is big!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.19,0:15:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're lucky we got to\Neat another potato today...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.66,0:15:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just once, I wanna eat until I'm full!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.06,0:16:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot! Don't tell Dad that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.80,0:16:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad gave up his dream of\Nbounty-hunting so he could support us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.77,0:16:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.44,0:16:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's an incredible hero across\Nthe sea on a big adventure,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.71,0:16:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I wonder if there's anything\Nthat exciting for us, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.41,0:16:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course there isn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.12,0:16:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna live our lives\Nwithout anything interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.72,0:16:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even Dad threw away his dream for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.79,0:16:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to spend our whole\Nlives in this withered land, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.56,0:16:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of glum look is that?!\NQuit complaining!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.56,0:16:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.07,0:16:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just you watch! I'm gonna\Ngo back to bounty-hunting!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.50,0:16:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to challenge\Nthat hero! Fire Fist Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.44,0:16:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'm gonna fight the world's\Ngreatest battle and come back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.45,0:16:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world's greatest battle\Nis too much for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.22,0:16:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We came to get you, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.66,0:17:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be silly. I'm the\Nworld's greatest bounty hunter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.89,0:17:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've fought epic battles with\Neveryone from Double Barrel Danny
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.86,0:17:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to Hellbattler Luther and they\Nall begged for their lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.67,0:17:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or so you plan, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.17,0:17:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You found me out, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.97,0:17:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. I'm a terrible\Nliar and a terrible father.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.41,0:17:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, there is one thing that's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.55,0:17:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the most insignificant person
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.25,0:17:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,can still challenge the world's\Ngreatest hero if he tries hard enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.69,0:17:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I wanted!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.12,0:17:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to show you two a grand dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.56,0:17:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Men need dreams burning\Ninside their hearts!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.56,0:17:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it means struggling every day,\Nnever give up! Stand tall!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.03,0:17:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Live every day with a laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.80,0:17:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you keep challenging the\Nimpossible, life will be paradise!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.94,0:17:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's no way to show that\Nwithout putting my life on the line!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.18,0:18:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! If you stand up,\Nthe path will always open!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.08,0:18:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.45,0:18:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now! Watch your father's\Nunconquerable spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.62,0:18:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I won't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.09,0:18:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not as long as I have an enormous\Ndream burning inside my heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.43,0:18:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Popo! The bazooka!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.90,0:18:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire Fist Ace! This is the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.58,0:18:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad! That's enough! No more!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.01,0:18:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dip! Chip!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.35,0:18:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We understand! We understand\Nwhat you're trying to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.82,0:18:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We stood up to hardship, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.82,0:18:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll live every day as hard as we can!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.05,0:18:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With you around,\Nwe're filled with courage!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.22,0:18:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I complained!\NI don't really care about food!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.83,0:18:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy just being with you, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.47,0:18:55.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--We love you, Dad!\N--We love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.24,0:18:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dip! Chip!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.74,0:19:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.39,0:19:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Gum-Gum...\N--I got this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.86,0:19:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire Fist!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.55,0:19:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad! Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.95,0:19:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.19,0:19:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.15,0:19:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Ace...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.39,0:19:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad protected us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.53,0:19:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, old guy. Did you die?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.33,0:19:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't be stupid...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.77,0:20:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As if I could really die and\Nleave my adorable sons behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.97,0:20:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scorpion-sama is invulnerable!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.91,0:20:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for coming to get\Nthis lowly father of yours...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.75,0:20:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go home. To the Badlands!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.82,0:20:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.43,0:20:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.63,0:20:28.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really leaving, Ace?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.20,0:20:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.40,0:20:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing as Blackbeard isn't in Alabasta,\NI have no reason to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.21,0:20:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Oh.\N--Where will you go next?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.48,0:20:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scorpion says there's a man\Nwho saw him in the west.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.75,0:20:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I'll check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.31,0:20:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.42,0:20:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Always hang on to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.15,0:20:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? It's just a scrap of paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.32,0:20:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That scrap of paper will bring you\Nand me together again sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.39,0:20:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.76,0:20:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You don't want it?\N--No, I'll keep it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.43,0:21:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's natural for a big brother to\Nworry about his bungling kid brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.73,0:21:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He might be a bit much for you to\Nhandle, but take good care of 'im.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.37,0:21:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.07,0:21:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy. When we next meet,\Nwe'll both be top pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.64,0:21:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.54,0:21:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to the top!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.15,0:21:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.62,0:21:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.52,0:21:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where's Ace?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.46,0:21:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.86,0:21:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire Fist Ace, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.13,0:21:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll see him again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.20,0:21:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I'm sure of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.18,0:21:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like the adventurers\NI dreamed of when I was a child
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.02,0:21:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I continue on to the ends of emotion
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.09,0:22:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I scoop up my hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.09,0:22:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the sand and time\Nthat spills from them
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.70,0:22:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,show me that this is\Nwhat I was born to do
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.71,0:22:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's continue swimming\Nat a near-tumbling speed
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.82,0:22:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until we wash up someday\Non a white sandy beach
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.56,0:22:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,no one knows about
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.18,0:22:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace-san certainly was\Na mysterious person.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.32,0:23:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I suppose he was!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.15,0:23:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! You ladies prefer mysterious men?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.35,0:23:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm enigmatic, too!\NMy left eye, for example!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.89,0:23:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what did he say?\NTranslate, Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.96,0:23:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey! They're gone!\N--Don't tell me they got separated?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.10,0:23:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.43,0:23:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Ruins and Lost Ways!\NVivi, Her Friends, and the Country's Form"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.70,0:23:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
